- [Contrast checker](https://contrast-checker.glitch.me/) - Built by designers from within Government.
- [Colour contrast checker](https://microsoftedge.microsoft.com/addons/detail/colour-contrast-checker/jkmnghgbaaoohmjdblniohhjnpjmnand) - Edge plugin to check web pages from within the browser.